{"tid":2335180,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–便利糖尿病人的一道研究","createTime":"2020-12-21T16:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T04:22:10.000Z","uid":38861,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"655e95a0960652454d1984e19c4c03453bfbfbb2","tid":2335180,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:03:16.000Z","msg":"血糖高企是糖尿病的其中之一的特徵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUs7b2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUs7b2Y.jpg&h=98703c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注射胰島素能加快身體細胞吸取血液糖份的速度，幫助降低血糖濃度，而前提當然是患者的身體細胞依然能對胰島素起上反應。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）常用的胰島素Glargine接近需要每日注射一次，有不少病人因嫌麻煩或其他原因沒能持之以恆注射，導致沒法完整地完成療程。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xb0w29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xb0w29.jpg&h=4f15c6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現今廠商開發了名為Icodec的胰島素，標榜只需一星期打一次，亦能達致體內胰島素每日平均的濃度與Glargine用家大致相同。<br />\n<br />\nIcodec經過一系列的結構改造，使其能夠與血液含量豐富的白蛋白(Albumin)結合，<br />\n達致在血液中緩慢釋放胰島素到達細胞的效果。<br />\n而且蛋白酶分解它的速度有所被調減，因此可以達致一劑過高濃度，而又能穩定地慢慢以低劑量的方式釋放到細胞裡頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）經過26星期的療程後，需要一日打一次的Glargine(122人)與只需一星期打一次的Icodec(125人)均能降低血糖濃度，而且兩者並無顯著的分別(Ref1)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apVTR3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapVTR3d.png&h=66d8fb74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若能招募更多人士確立其安全性及功效，只需一星期打一次的Icodec將來或許能打入市場，有助便利病人完成整個療程。<br />\n<br />\n但這並不代表Glargine的市場會完全地被取締，當用家需要因每日所需調整胰島素濃度的話，Glargine始終是較佳的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。</span><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e244aeaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a640efd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=440ba1fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1: <a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJMoa2022474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2022474&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=5b118ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJMoa2022474</a>"},{"pid":"1a27680e63b86a4ba9994026e02937111e9b2a75","tid":2335180,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:08:56.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86ebdac1cd016b440259dc3e319e077313d9cf3","tid":2335180,"uid":75448,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"希望有多d方法可以免除針藥之苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e33314e776db57a2c