atxm/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e58f996bb4b4e2afd28deb893c78af642240b9","tid":2335180,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f92b35cd8dd9b48485e35d845bb3674d705c54a7","tid":2335180,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"有咩副作用架"},{"pid":"cd1629f279441931567266de9d16aceac0c9405a","tid":2335180,"uid":319820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"篇paper話會易d輕微血糖低wor"},{"pid":"3617c915e049cc4d177fc7da4fb174536774b337","tid":2335180,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bccdce26a30366aaabe8db22fda5da1a8851253","tid":2335180,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab17526364ebb30b4d9e5ac1f5c509914bcf8860","tid":2335180,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"long time no c<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b917d8d81c9b2a4a7e9bc89a7fa971d13aa15e19","tid":2335180,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e0f5625cf604909b08c8780f404729191c41cd","tid":2335180,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"幾年前見過話有人研究緊口服胰島素，研發成功後只需定時食藥就得唔使日日打針，話應該過多幾年可以臨床試驗，唔知有無呢方便跟進資料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef662f2d52ccb9eb1549003be51890cd01f0de85","tid":2335180,"uid":75448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"補充下<br />\n糖尿病人應該都有1,2型<br />\n1型係天生就完全無胰島素，永遠要打胰島素，有長效既針佢地會舒服好多。<br />\n<br />\n2型係前期唔洗打針，控制飲食同食藥控制，因為身體仲有胰島素產生，除非有異常例如身體有嚴重炎症或做完手術，可能就需要打胰島素。<br />\n後期病人身體胰島素唔太夠/冇胰島素生產，藥物幫助唔到身體分泌胰島素，先要依賴注射胰島素。"},{"pid":"7f23cbbd3dbc92aadf21e1b920a21905197fd153","tid":2335180,"uid":172172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"深入淺出師近排咁高產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86259ab1c4d3e3e336c25215c339dbf288b4f5a4","tid":2335180,"uid":362035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef662f2d52ccb9eb1549003be51890cd01f0de85","tid":2335180,"uid":75448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"補充下<br />\n糖尿病人應該都有1,2型<br />\n1型係天生就完全無胰島素，永遠要打胰島素，有長效既針佢地會舒服好多。<br />\n<br />\n2型係前期唔洗打針，控制飲食同食藥控制，因為身體仲有胰島素產生，除非有異常例如身體有嚴重炎症或做完手術，可能就需要打胰島素。<br />\n後期病人身體胰島素唔太夠/冇胰島素生產，藥物幫助唔到身體分泌胰島素，先要依賴注射胰島素。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"正想補充<br />\n自己有一型糖尿，後生既，隻藥的確會方便咗我哋生活，自己一日打4次，三餐前+臨瞓，所以自己考慮到穩定性。隻藥未必啱小朋友+青年，荷爾蒙會影響血糖控制，短效藥啱我哋多d，避免成日低血糖。<br />\n<br />\n一直都望緊，未來可能裝粒野落手臂，用手機check到血糖 (宜家已經有)，同係手機㩒打幾多度胰島素落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00900982a8f0a77db3b1e8f6f958f721f4d75adf","tid":2335180,"uid":109706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"高質文，得閒可以講解下dna預早知幾時有病既原理同準確率"},{"pid":"285d2fd604110b23167f6339ea7e6c9ff9c2bf5b","tid":2335180,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b86ebdac1cd016b440259dc3e319e077313d9cf3","tid":2335180,"uid":75448,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"希望有多d方法可以免除針藥之苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"